reviews.title: Don\'t use this App
reviews.comment: This company is either totally incompetent or has gone bankrupt. I\'ve been waiting for over three weeks now for its promise of two days to authorize my account application. Do NOT download this product.  What\'s wrong with these guys. Signing up customers is not rocket science. It\'s a terrible business model to keep customers waiting for weeks for something that could happen over night in a more professionally run company. Wake up, guys. Look at the business you are scaring off with your lazy attitudes towards us.
reviews.author: A Google User
